{"h2dbfc458ga9fbg492bgb6d4g08f743fb59ff": ["There you are. I've been waiting.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "97ccbb56-1268-dafa-8da1-ad456792a01b"], "hffb5435dg52deg4d85ga0f6gd19c56bab82c": ["Waiting since the moment I set eyes on you.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "b0c650ee-81e9-97b4-ca6d-7e48899b2414"], "h988e06a1gd0cfg4688gba77gdeb464ecc503": ["Waiting to have you.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "144b1dc8-7d3e-21d3-91e4-609ded7ab4dd"], "hfab96083ge4dag4992gbcf7gd8fd4d3748d3": ["You don't have me yet.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "33cdf653-64aa-3e56-2e28-bc0095ce157c"], "h17733c78gc6bbg4a85gae73g603eb3abc910": ["Don't I? You're here. And I don't think you want to talk.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "eddb0091-406c-b140-0412-69d4b0e2641c"], "h0e2a65c6g04c5g48f3g9ec6g16fb3228e3c0": ["I think you want to be known. To be tasted.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "11fe5070-eb20-a35d-e6ae-9214d168b7a3"], "hc9e9384cgd28cg47d1g8bf1g8124e2ba015f": ["And what do you want?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "ae6e3a71-b06b-d30b-6029-840298479937"], "hbdd4c4b2g99fag426dga2aag3df4d5f1b56b": ["What do any of us want? Pleasure.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "021a3bc9-6091-90de-b864-7a41391b3ab5"], "hd6eefaa0g416eg4441gbcf8g484505f1839d": ["Yours. Mine. Our collective ecstasy.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "6672df2d-22f2-74d1-d51e-349005698a59"], "h5bcdace0g5dd5g4b4dg8e2ag455d4b267dd7": ["That's what you want, isn't it? To lose yourself in me?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "ea7c56a3-512c-cca1-4b4b-244c748f3d1b"], "h2eb67e2bg853eg40e3g97e1gba8ab0793ffa": ["<i>Nod.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "bcdfcba1-ccb6-d8a4-4252-0460899d7dc5"], "h08f33e2eg68dfg4ce1g8be8gdc98429820f2": ["I thought so.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "f2f3d43f-a215-bfbc-94b9-dcc9552f5cca"], "h1cd12f70gf05ag4442g87e4gfc4f3a15663e": ["*His skin is cool to the touch, his kiss bracing. You lean in and he pulls you closer.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "d5108313-c5db-59cd-3722-62b7fc2b2044"], "h01348cd4ga0bag4576g8afegb04ecf8e3969": ["<i>Relax. Enjoy yourself.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "e5ff2d24-fe21-117c-604a-cca03305f1c4"], "h747df673gecb8g47adg8940gfa3c7342d11c": ["Interesting scars. Where'd you get them?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "4eccb931-e338-8128-9156-bbe0b2a2685e"], "h1508d52dg3ee5g42cagb8b9g1a292ebe5d6d": ["That's Cazador's poem on your back? Written in scars?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "c7d4d854-4260-672b-f735-9d104f360295"], "h6217575cgd4f4g41acg9ff3ge4c1be3adccb": ["Not staying for a cuddle?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "7c1c84ec-40b3-45e8-fd9e-4c014ec62c74"], "h674276a1g8e43g451bg8512ge4fd80230370": ["You sleep light. I thought you'd be exhausted after last night.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "4fd6b0f9-9e76-79bb-cc56-15f3eabc8d66"], "h7180f361g22b0g4c31g8698g5d015413163e": ["You weren't <i>that </i>good.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "42b8e8fb-6ecf-fa13-7864-215e282dba3c"], "h52e752e8g2231g40e3g9e68g4211f691fdf5": ["How dare you - I'm a consummate lover.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "d09b24e1-46ba-29e7-60a6-8c612692bb87"], "hc0e57493g2752g4789ga191gd6df78e7ac21": ["I was holding back, if anything. Worried that I might... lose control.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "76835c96-9ef8-c4ee-f7b1-c7c80a1bb605"], "h03035aa0gf222g4902gb547g3332fbedfd41": ["Delicious as you were, I didn't want to go too far.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "e89eec97-bf67-b8a7-5557-8f76e286c921"], "h84184ac0gf40fg4619gba37ga50d66c96218": ["Now, shall we get on? I want to go before the goblins start waking up.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "446c07f8-f03f-2ca5-20c2-23af1ea5cb4e"], "h7ce9ccb0g6e65g4866ga710gcc3499105076": ["I wanted to ask about your scars first. Where'd you get them?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "dbb85669-c074-9d8e-635d-8af9128b75bb"], "ha618bb1bgb3f0g4734g8913ga5633bfdd5b4": ["My past isn't exactly a happy story.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "1230e557-f315-b308-f4ab-5311eaf7c11b"], "h713367a2g8aecg43c2gae6bga4a506a0b8cf": ["I told you that I was a magistrate in Baldur's Gate, but that's only part of it.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "157c90f6-a17f-3e27-a4a8-60a0219e2d8e"], "hc2e6b696gb93bg46f9g945fgc66acde718a4": ["The mind flayers weren't my first kidnapping. A long time ago, I crossed Cazador - a powerful man in Baldur's Gate.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "5d180305-8131-7336-223e-be84194cafea"], "h84a7a36eg5d9ag489ega5f8g1aa5ff836100": ["He captured me. Kept me for years as his slave.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "b73fb9c3-677a-1f70-72fa-1642f7f17cd7"], "h4f8ef4d3ge9a4g459ega593g567c7ae8c0fb": ["And he gave you those scars?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "b1d0b14a-af71-bfeb-fb0e-52a1c3400b4e"], "h9236fd2cg8707g4f69g89e8gbaa07bcdfa13": ["Yes. It's a poem. My old master considered himself quite the artist.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "0ba7667a-f1fb-8e73-69f7-a9cafca04a91"], "hcea5e4b3g5b1bg46d7gaa1dg6b22a6020b19": ["I'm sorry, that sounds terrible.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "3374f2bd-feb8-8036-ce7f-33b6d6937685"], "hade5ddc3g13deg4e28g8b42gf53d6f749223": ["It was.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "390f4abf-d438-ea0a-8971-d100a09a0c87"], "hf7199abdga4abg48efgbd02g4b7f84cd41c7": ["Cazador said the scars were his gift. A poem to carry with me.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "4fa73600-54ff-9ede-1e6f-01aeccde64de"], "hb3e676d0g4042g46e2g8de2gb5350ed123e5": ["How did you escape?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "f2446076-10b4-dbb2-3578-7c44abbd31a3"], "hb9ba2223g0d3fg4e42ga125g37ca2a1f191f": ["That was my second kidnapping, when the mind flayers snatched me up.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "9200c7f3-4d14-2c1b-ede0-32a2ea743c72"], "h935cd81fgf7a2g4beag9cebg4142573ce494": ["Not a great improvement, but at least they didn't mutilate me.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "7ce8b2b2-1757-4a34-c24b-e75c763a5591"], "hf1ef9b69g69a1g48faga83eg0d3b23a1b189": ["It's a poem. A gift from Cazador. He considered himself quite the artist and used his slaves as a canvas.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "4bc374fe-9e18-8a95-19eb-4ca47b1b5e49"], "h56e09367g733eg4eb2gbbf8g76cfde57b894": ["He composed and carved that one over the course of a night. He made a lot of revisions as he went.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "1b87d59b-3f46-502b-b0d2-97814b4d70c7"], "h887b0343gc216g4765g8f45g79cab43a66a6": ["*You recall the sharp, complex lines of the script - it was written in the language of the Hells.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "767b4228-c6a0-5ba6-fb81-f1c2fcbb67a7"], "h27274b79gd847g4a04g8beeg80929c8bf621": ["Why did he write it in Infernal?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "863682ee-b3a9-e240-f94a-3e5dfcd5f7aa"], "h6251c618gfe70g45e4gbc1bg3624dc1592c9": ["Infernal? I... who knows? The bastard was insane.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "f8d1d487-ede3-75d8-6a48-0ac0cc7609c4"], "h2215ecf2g0163g40aag9cb6g918650f5c3c3": ["Anyway, enough pillow talk. Let's go, before the goblins start stirring.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "2108a0a9-58f0-a56b-8357-88663a2484c3"], "he52aea7bg16eag43e2g9ac8g9ef141f4b12f": ["Anyway, enough pillow talk. Let's go, before the tieflings drag us into another mess.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "7907d6d3-21fb-e094-6bd5-16f2f513124c"], "hf9774a22g23bdg4750g9c0dge82e497d1f64": ["What does it say?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "4fa064c7-ba66-5331-83db-ab3c4cbf5c06"], "h477c2ee6g11feg4665g84bag4acce72135c0": ["I don't know, it's not like I can look in a mirror and see.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "9821b6e7-0b68-2879-f65e-14a50ed516a0"], "h626b4311g2e12g4f32gad57g843e5c68d3b1": ["Can I see?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "aca512a0-61d6-1c0e-768d-3b06e6e33378"], "he43bc0c0g7a46g43a7g9791g2c5c705bb637": ["You've seen enough already.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "f1059854-a8eb-72ec-c458-30fea96be04c"], "h4a83e59cg5481g4d1cgb3c6g3db9d3b93a39": ["And if I can't see it, you certainly can't.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "3f5cbb51-0129-5a71-d2d1-e34ea47c1d8c"], "h9363cb7cga41bg45e7ga929g5f80699d637a": ["You've <i>never </i>seen it?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "0668acbf-3229-ceec-5a32-0542aa72386f"], "h951e315eg2c15g48c7gab47g0206bc0c576b": ["Well I can't just check in a mirror, can I?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "99a77bff-e65f-b16b-9f00-45a3bf4385e2"], "h23575e92g88f8g4dd8g9f4fga0165c5f4748": ["It doesn't matter anyway. Whatever the bastard wrote, it won't change anything he did to me.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "8637727c-1e30-05ad-ca4c-f06cb4213370"], "h67dbca78g71e0g47dbgb8e1g620411b8acc2": ["Now let's go. We've wasted enough time already.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "a1cf2e2f-e93e-5652-1b32-0b5d12a08717"], "hf2f9c462g5c02g4c4ag8c70g47dd398c9b6b": ["Now let's go, before I regret my restraint last night.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "d2555202-97b1-f1a4-0101-c90efacc6c3b"], "h5a2f79b5gdd04g466fgaa07g408736d05ab0": ["It's written in Infernal. I could read it, if you like?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "580d0e6b-e9e3-4e1c-1012-452d921b0286"], "h92655d31gcb29g4613g9f53gcd05c6bf0069": ["Infernal? I - no. It doesn't matter what it says.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "9e63de99-1d30-9f88-d68d-acade68d8dc0"], "h87dd04c0g9dd2g4aa0g8c37g82e494423d5e": ["Whatever the bastard wrote, it won't change what he did to me.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "f6c679a3-b6b8-034c-e3ed-c9edd54d4912"], "h63d5c86egeb1dg46e2gb353ge8e8b5384ca4": ["Aren't you curious what it says?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "a497ac81-f160-4e2e-21b2-ee3b0a83c987"], "h711450c9g1e50g451dg8f7cgc6e25dfed84b": ["No! I'm not.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "a0edbd7d-57a2-5d74-132f-ae422423a39d"], "h31d1aadcgb0a6g420cga327g53caf957fa1f": ["All right. Let's get moving, then.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "6a76b5d7-afa1-ad4c-3884-a4c8791d3abf"], "h6671bfb0g364ag4893gbf4dg480e1aaaf436": ["Finally. I'm just glad your performance last night was better than your pillow talk.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "3ed15113-89c7-9fe6-9f3a-cc09ccc23581"], "hbc057960g2c7fg455cg8279g30ad94418f55": ["Is it a good poem, at least?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "85ef3e46-4625-190f-040c-478b641ef39a"], "ha4d9bc4cg7867g4401gb10bg92a421857c1f": ["I don't know. I never asked for a reading and it's not like I can just peek in a mirror to see.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "0e00d54a-4584-b188-4b35-df1e49a376fe"], "h2e0887c5ga8c0g41c7g9476ge274d415a2e4": ["Why did he write it in Infernal? That's normally a devil's language.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "085459cc-51ac-c3d0-d313-6e3821c8028a"], "h2db50468g9ff6g41abgaef2g89c3ab7aed7d": ["It's a poem. A gift from my old master, Cazador. He considered himself quite the artist and used his slaves as a canvas.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "9279afe4-980d-c726-38a2-1baf3145c349"], "h71a3c47fga60cg4515ga576g48ae1773bff4": ["I wanted to ask about your scars first. Is that Cazador's poem?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "d166eea8-dc77-dbbb-6a3a-e7b82df4ac79"], "h0f2a8f2dg18b3g43a2g839cg2c9ce5eb4989": ["Yes. What of it?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "dd4499a5-0730-80b1-4327-23bbd68b3bd9"], "h03201601gd5c2g40eag9f73g1412ddb06c9f": ["Sure, let's go.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "bb37699e-5a6c-750b-70d4-838f551abe56"], "ha0aca23ag197dg4a7cgbbeag310dd670e23d": ["And don't feel the need to brag to the others about our little tryst. ", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "e5775904-9247-b759-542c-862f2c9e6338"], "h8f11322egff2bg45ecgbe7bgbf2af9937b7b": ["Given the noise you made last night, I'm sure they already know.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "129bbb3d-b539-cbfa-6a6c-c7890a3a5eaf"], "h870c07e4g747ag40efg992fg6362073e0425": ["Now, shall we get on? I want to go before anyone else thanks me for saving their tails.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "a0c4b2a7-fd09-c45e-247f-70c906318bbb"], "ha022ed0bg00ecg4eadg80e0g5cc517640ce9": ["Did you enjoy it? It felt like you weren't fully there.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "6eeaf32a-849b-c86d-d933-f73d51486a96"], "ha1f105e0gc66fg4afdgb25cge4d948c587d7": ["I was holding back a little, it's true. I didn't want to lose control.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "38d22924-4f73-9e02-09a9-36934e98d5bb"], "hab90e24cge6b9g41eeg9cd4g1d479d131f4e": ["I could always go again.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "e83fe5e1-4240-de6b-1c75-70488cf36af6"], "h70f86e39g9a31g4b2eg89cfgf71d003d9121": ["Tempting, but this might not be the time or the place. ", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "d0094ca5-9b30-db25-a434-beff3c0eeb84"], "h41751c1cg6ee3g4370g8937g4da8849871a6": ["Time to get going.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "72a2f70a-35eb-a138-360b-f26ce43ead5c"], "hd8bd2e76g1bb6g4405g978fg5d11c639f685": ["My thoughts exactly. I want to go before the goblins start waking up.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "78ae30ae-158e-897f-e7f1-8b4ca8eb2689"], "h69700262g8463g4cfcg976dg32f69d325ced": ["My thoughts exactly. I want to go before anyone else thanks me for saving their tails.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "fb6a2678-5b21-3b31-7aaa-3f63e311e63d"], "hd0c7d22bg0236g4d5cg8276g36977800f9ff": ["<i>Relax . Enjoy yourself. Trust him not to bite you.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "ddd02f3e-70e2-e33a-d065-848bbaa95b1e"], "h5413b3aagf05cg4be9ga2afgc0d34983fb05": ["<i>Roll playfully and offer him your neck.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "1755a863-d1af-54e1-c5a7-0347d30ed5d0"], "hb4075261g78a8g43c1gbd87gf19af62a1dd3": ["Keep those teeth away from me!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "f38b231a-0990-958c-7964-1048dcee6f8f"], "hfc6dffd2gf8ccg469eg8d8fgb84cde2cb59e": ["Really? I thought we had an understanding. A connection.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "0f31fb09-48c9-e879-ee95-c9652ba9321c"], "ha677b3f7gea4fg4d87gb433gc7d8466e8479": ["It seems I was wrong. Pity. You look delicious in the moonlight.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "458d155f-2db2-2b3f-98ae-3f1eba52240c"], "h01bff877g6632g48b6g9229ge62aeb125f8a": ["I wasn't going to bite you. I told you this was about pleasure, not hunger.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "688fb123-6c18-9cfc-4754-3ce95cbe55ae"], "habe71cb6g6667g458ag833egb3d1a66f9456": ["But if you don't trust me, then I guess even that's off the table.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "b20f8905-9ffb-2ff8-198c-762a6cee64eb"], "h4a30b2aagd193g409fg96d3gd0a3b5705118": ["I wasn't going to bite you. I'm here because I thought we'd have a little fun.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "8af7fb92-cee8-662e-8bed-4e4b7806b671"], "h5ea9b429g1ffdg4fd8gbf50g44bcf14bb780": ["Wait, we're moving too fast.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "2be1b9f1-fd2a-be64-8434-6e54c621c350"], "h66cac7e6g69b1g411dg9923g9667c163ba3e": ["*His skin is cool to the touch, his kiss bracing. You lean in and he pulls you closer.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "bd5d8aa6-4542-6258-1b12-05f16b77d1f6"], "h80f1a30ag3309g405bg9aceg29e1a57c9ab8": ["I want to have fun - that's it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "e5f70753-45f2-b2e4-5b46-fad654ec82fc"], "h26bbedf2gcac5g4d5cgb470g94e2d8073f6a": ["Then let's have some fun.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "4024979f-22bb-ad8e-e399-d349eb47f1da"], "hc987ab81g6411g4bb3gbb71g869367dc6128": ["No, I don't want this.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "04fd622d-23ff-b912-f38a-7c3ca13cd7bc"], "h011860bag8fa1g4bedg8e9bgd7cf89fbaf90": ["Then what are you doing here?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "e2be5da1-79f8-116a-7db3-c96b9452aa3c"], "h3da7c478gf202g4931g8af6gcbb13ac69cb4": ["I thought we had an understanding, but I guess I'll just entertain myself tonight.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "a016aed7-1148-2616-576c-3626ad432e8c"], "h6b845a9cg642dg4fbdg9f20gf6fa7978f715": ["<i>Grin and let him kiss you.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "c43caf92-7d4f-03f1-b33a-00ff10d7143e"], "ha3e56bf1gbc15g4f63ga065gd5ecde4989b9": ["*His skin is cool to the touch, his kiss bracing. You lean in and he pulls you closer.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "fb1cd4a1-1544-7307-fd88-3fce899c3df4"], "h413ba053g7405g4e3cg8583ge077711de9ae": ["*His skin is cool to the touch, his kiss bracing. You lean in and he pulls you closer.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "fda60569-4d22-4186-52bf-6b190e0fded4"], "h0ea37178g0e7bg4066g9c0bgbedfc9322355": ["Try to 'taste' me and I'll incinerate you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "118353e2-2543-d1b4-0fba-4dc0d05d5e07"], "ha6b7aed5g18a6g4735gaf9agfd741e44ed9c": ["Try to 'taste' me and I'll blast you with enough divine energy to turn you to ash.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "118353e2-2543-d1b4-0fba-4dc0d05d5e07"], "h7b297e58gd494g4853g850dg4c96bf293c60": ["Try to 'taste' me and I'll kill you where you stand.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "118353e2-2543-d1b4-0fba-4dc0d05d5e07"], "hab175a77gf417g4008g8537gded86532598b": ["This isn't about hunger. It's about pleasure.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "b0073a48-872f-5a61-1815-18b6759718d3"], "h852a1282gcff3g4c79g86e8gb27c9acfcb47": ["Tasted? I'm not some snack.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "6b43d213-8e17-7280-62de-d71d67d3be7f"], "h9e9cdd61gf8e7g460fga4deg629396383cc8": ["<i>Say nothing, just let him kiss you.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "639e58fe-1ecf-a2ad-2871-a902283d7a46"], "h7a59d512g5a6cg4fb6gbd68gb26bdfea6c26": ["Hold on - I'm not sure about this.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithAstarion.html", "c00ebeb5-a1ba-1eea-fa73-c3efcb01e1e5"]}